{%- assign collection = collections[section.settings.collection] -%}
{%- assign product_limit = section.settings.grid | times: section.settings.rows -%}

{%- comment -%}
  2026-05-19 (bd 2i8b.35): lazy-render DISABLED, always render full content.

  The earlier `{%- if request.design_mode or request.page_type == null -%}` gate
  intended to render full content for editor preview AND for Section Rendering
  API requests, then emit a tiny placeholder for normal pageloads (deferred
  fetch via IntersectionObserver). But Shopify does NOT null out
  request.page_type for ?section_id= requests — the API returned the
  placeholder. We tried two JS-side workarounds:

  - 2i8b.30: extract <noscript> fallback content via innerHTML — collapsed
    nested per-product <noscript>s, dropping 11/12 cards.
  - 2i8b.34: DOMParser-based extraction (parses noscript children as DOM).
    Got the 12 cards visible inside the section, BUT also left ~5-11 orphan
    `.product-grid-item` elements as direct children of <main> — each
    1280px wide (no grid constraint). Operator perceived these as "giant
    sliders" because they bled out of the grid.

  Disabling lazy-render server-side eliminates the entire bug class. The
  perf trade-off: each homepage-collection section renders its full grid
  HTML on initial pageload instead of deferring to IntersectionObserver.
  For HairMNL's 8 homepage sections at 12 products × ~3KB each = ~290KB
  of HTML, that's an acceptable increase to ship a working page.

  If lazy-render is needed in future, the proper Liquid-side detection
  needs to be solved (request.page_type doesn't work; section.location
  doesn't help either). Until then: always full-render.

  brand-collection.liquid and related.liquid use the same pattern — they
  should be updated similarly if their lazy-render shows the same symptom.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if true -%}
  <div
    class="homepage-collection {{ section.settings.bg }}"
    data-section-id="{{ section.id }}"
    data-section-type="collection-row">
    <div class="wrapper">
      {% if section.settings.title != blank %}
        <h2 class="home__subtitle">{{ section.settings.title | escape }}</h2>
      {% endif %}
      <div
        class="js-grid"
        data-grid-large="{{ section.settings.grid }}"
        data-grid-small="2">
        <!-- /snippets/product-grid-item.liquid -->
        {% for product in collection.products limit: product_limit %}
          {% render 'product-grid-item', product: product %}
        {% else %}
          {% render 'onboarding-product-grid-item', limit: product_limit %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% if section.settings.show_view_all %}
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="{{ collection.url }}" class="btn--outline uppercase">
            {{ 'collections.general.view_all' | t }}
          </a>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .homepage-collection {
      padding-top: {{ section.settings.desktop_padding_top }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.desktop_padding_bottom }}px;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 640px) {
      #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .homepage-collection {
        padding-top: {{ section.settings.mobile_padding_top }}px;
        padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.mobile_padding_bottom }}px;
      }
    }
  </style>

{%- else -%}
  {%- comment -%}
    Normal pageload: emit a lightweight placeholder that IntersectionObserver
    will replace with the real section content when it approaches the viewport.
    <noscript> fallback ensures crawlers and non-JS users see the content.
  {%- endcomment -%}
  <div
    class="homepage-collection {{ section.settings.bg }}"
    data-section-id="{{ section.id }}"
    data-section-type="collection-row"
    data-lazy-render
    data-lazy-url="/?section_id={{ section.id }}">
    <!-- placeholder — content will be fetched via Section Rendering API when
         IntersectionObserver triggers. See hairmnl-common.js lazy-render init. -->
  </div>
  <noscript>
    <div
      class="homepage-collection {{ section.settings.bg }}"
      data-section-id="{{ section.id }}"
      data-section-type="collection-row">
      <div class="wrapper">
        {% if section.settings.title != blank %}
          <h2 class="home__subtitle">{{ section.settings.title | escape }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        <div
          class="js-grid"
          data-grid-large="{{ section.settings.grid }}"
          data-grid-small="2">
          <!-- /snippets/product-grid-item.liquid -->
          {% for product in collection.products limit: product_limit %}
            {% render 'product-grid-item', product: product %}
          {% else %}
            {% render 'onboarding-product-grid-item', limit: product_limit %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% if section.settings.show_view_all %}
          <div class="text-center">
            <a href="{{ collection.url }}" class="btn--outline uppercase">
              {{ 'collections.general.view_all' | t }}
            </a>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </noscript>

  <style>
    #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .homepage-collection {
      padding-top: {{ section.settings.desktop_padding_top }}px;
      padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.desktop_padding_bottom }}px;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 640px) {
      #shopify-section-{{ section.id }} .homepage-collection {
        padding-top: {{ section.settings.mobile_padding_top }}px;
        padding-bottom: {{ section.settings.mobile_padding_bottom }}px;
      }
    }
  </style>
{%- endif -%}

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Featured collection",
    "settings": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "title",
        "label": "Heading",
        "default": "Featured Products"
      },
      {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "title_font_size",
        "min": 1,
        "max": 40,
        "step": 1,
        "label": "Title font size",
        "default": 28
      },
      {
        "id": "collection",
        "type": "collection",
        "label": "Collection"
      },
      {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "grid",
        "min": 1,
        "max": 6,
        "step": 1,
        "label": "Products per row",
        "default": 3
      }, {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "rows",
        "min": 1,
        "max": 8,
        "step": 1,
        "label": "Number of rows",
        "default": 1
      }, {
        "type": "select",
        "id": "bg",
        "label": "Background color",
        "default": "palette--light bg--neutral",
        "options": [
          {
            "value": "palette--light bg--neutral",
            "label": "Default"
          }, {
            "value": "palette--light bg--accent",
            "label": "Light"
          }, {
            "value": "palette--dark bg--invert",
            "label": "Dark"
          }, {
            "value": "palette--dark bg--invert--accent",
            "label": "Dark accent"
          }
        ]
      }, {
        "type": "checkbox",
        "id": "show_view_all",
        "label": "Show 'View all' button",
        "default": false
      }, {
        "type": "header",
        "content": "Section Padding(Desktop)"
      }, {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "desktop_padding_top",
        "min": 0,
        "max": 200,
        "step": 4,
        "unit": "px",
        "label": "Padding top(Desktop)",
        "default": 96
      }, {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "desktop_padding_bottom",
        "min": 0,
        "max": 200,
        "step": 4,
        "unit": "px",
        "label": "Padding bottom(Desktop)",
        "default": 96
      },
      {
        "type": "header",
        "content": "Section Padding(Mobile)"
      }, {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "mobile_padding_top",
        "min": 0,
        "max": 200,
        "step": 4,
        "unit": "px",
        "label": "Padding top(Mobile)",
        "default": 96
      }, {
        "type": "range",
        "id": "mobile_padding_bottom",
        "min": 0,
        "max": 200,
        "step": 4,
        "unit": "px",
        "label": "Padding bottom(Mobile)",
        "default": 96
      }
    ],
    "presets": [
      {
        "name": "Featured collection",
        "category": "Collection"
      }
    ]
  }
{% endschema %}